title: ‘Sounds of the Stadium’ Concert to Feature James Bond Tunes (The University of Findlay)
text: ( Source : The University of Findlay ) The 8th Annual Oiler Brass concert, 'Sounds of the Stadium ,' directed by Richard Napierala, will take place at 2 p.m. Sunday, Nov. 3 in Winebrenner Theological Seminary 's TLB Auditorium . Admission is free
